  "story": "A joyful Hindi Sunday School bhajan that has introduced generations of children to the love of Jesus. This simple, catchy song is a staple of children's church programs and Vacation Bible School across Hindi-speaking India. Its easy-to-remember lyrics and cheerful tune make it a favorite among the youngest believers.",
